message.text: Can iron pickaxe be used to mine diamonds?

generation: Yes, an iron pickaxe can be used to mine diamonds. However, it is not the most efficient tool for mining diamonds. A diamond pickaxe is the fastest and most durable tool for mining diamonds. Using an iron pickaxe will still allow you to mine diamonds, but it will take longer and the pickaxe will wear out more quickly.
